getItemRoleName

public java.lang.String getItemRoleName()

getStatus

public java.lang.String getStatus()
Returns:
Acceptance status. Either "pending" or "accepted".

getItemType

public java.lang.String getItemType()
Returns:
The type of item. Either Box.TYPE_FILE or Box.TYPE_FOLDER. As there is currently no way to invite collaborators to files, this will always be Box.TYPE_FOLDER.

getItemId

public long getItemId()
Returns:
The id of the item being collaborated on. As there is currently no way to invite collaborators to files, this will always be the folder id.

getItemName

public java.lang.String getItemName()
Returns:
The name of the item being collaborated on. As there is currently no way to invite collaborators to files, this will always be the folder name.

getItemUserId
